  "title": "Circular Progress Ring",
  "summary": "A determinate SVG ring that fills to a percentage via stroke-dashoffset, with a live label.",
  "description": "An SVG circle whose stroke-dasharray equals its circumference; animating stroke-dashoffset reveals the arc proportional to a percentage — the standard circular progress meter.",
